snippet.title: Level Up Bus Gameplay Walkthrough
snippet.description:
About The Game:

Dodge overtaking and show your superb driving skills!

This is a very fun overtaking game!

Take your passengers, experience the thrill of racing, and simulate the thrill of actual driving!

Avoid red high-level vehicles, devour green vehicles, and send your passengers to the finish line safely! So enjoy the ride!

Just press and hold to overtake, release to return to lane.


Download For Android:

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.game.bus.rush
